<span class="OUT">fuel_level       :  </span><span class="OK">74.2%</span>
<span class="CC"># All data in CLEARTEXT — zero encryption — readable by anyone on the network</span></pre>

      <div class="eye V" style="margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:20px;">Step C — Injecting False Sensor Data</div>
