      <p class="BM" style="margin-bottom:12px;">The injection script (inject_v2.py) connects directly to the SCADA server's TCP port 5020 — which requires <strong>zero authentication</strong> — and sends crafted sensor readings. The values are chosen to be believable enough to avoid instant suspicion, but dangerous: 38,500 kg is 240% over the crane's safe capacity. Without SIEM, this injection would be completely invisible to operators.</p>
