          <span class="Is">container_temp   </span><span class="Ia">→</span> <span class="Io">3.54°C</span><span class="Ia">injected as</span><span class="If">87.5°C</span> <span class="Ist">⚠ CARGO DESTRUCTION SIMULATED</span><br>
