    <h1 class="DL">LATERAL <span class="tc">MOVE</span><br>& PIVOT</h1>
    <div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;letter-spacing:3px;color:var(--fog);margin-top:8px;text-transform:uppercase;">SSH Pivot · sudo Escalation · Root Shell · Backdoor · Forensics</div>
